This message contains information on the timing of the next pulse at the TIMEPULSE0output. The recommended configuration when using this message is to set both themeasurement rate (CFG-RATE) and the timepulse frequency (CFG-TP5) to 1Hz. For moreinformation see section Time pulse.TIMEPULSE0 and this message are not available from DR products using the dedicated I2Csensor interface, including NEO-M8L and NEO-M8U modules
